Installation instructions:

DEPENDENCIES
============

- SQLite must be insalled on the Edison. To do so, download from http://www.sqlite.org/. Shell commands './configure; make; make install' will install everything to the Edison.

- Pysqlite2 must also be installed on the Edison. Download from https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pysqlite. Shell commands 'python setup.py build' followed by 'python setup.py install' will install everything to the Edison.


INITIAL SETUP
=============

- If this is the first time installing the web server, shell command 'python create_db.py'.


RUNNING THE WEB SERVER
======================

- Run shell command 'python web_server.py'.